ical backgrounds of these early collections.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aAltes Testament. 4aProphet. 4aZwölfprophetenbuch. 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh  aBook of the twelve prophets.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE/RELIGIONSWISS./JUDAISTIK  2006z9783110277043oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311018996440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311092293640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110922936423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110922936/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2006  aZDB-23-DGGb2006  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014